			<div class="content" id="post-content-4719590">
									

<p>Read through it all, and I have some questions&#8212; not on the story side, but on the creation side.</p>
<ul>
<li>What sort of precautions did you take while shooting the footage? Like, did you have a spotter outside the place where you took it to come look for you if you didn't come up after X amount of time? Did you inform people where you were going? Put down markers with luminescent chalk?</li>
<li>What actually is this place? I don't expect you to doxx yourself by telling me <em>where</em> it is.</li>
<li>What was the song used in the last video? I know I heard lyrics or words at the time described in the OP, but I can't make it out.</li>
</ul>
<p>I'm trying to sit through the end right now, in a well-lit room. Scared AF.</p>

