			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4720391">
									

<p>You know, think on it, I almost don't care about these questions. All this build up to reach &quot;it wasn't John's&quot;, and a creepy and long and dark video&#8230; The reasons could be mundane, there could be nothing strange. The corpse could be someone random, meaningless, insignificant and unrelated, but the horror of dying alone in the wet and dark remains and dominates.</p>

