			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4720403">
									

<p>That's more or less what I was aiming for. Nevertheless, there <em>is</em> an answer, but&#8230; like &#8212; in so many of these cases &#8212; the answer feels (to me, anyway) a bit&#8230; &quot;underwhelming&quot;. It's only there to make sure I write with some consistency (to make it 'feel' more credible).</p>
<p>The aim was to create a sense of loneliness, cold, and dread &#8212; the sense of dying alone in a place where no one will ever find you or your body.</p>

